Package: snakemakeR
Title: Generate Snakemake S4 Snippets for R Scripts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Amel", "Zulji", , "zuljiamel1991@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Helpers for drafting Snakemake S4 boilerplate alongside R
    analyses. Use 'create_sm_s4()' to retrieve the snippet as text, or
    'paste_sm_s4_code()' to insert it directly into the active RStudio editor.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
